  <brief_title>Beetroot Enriched Bread, Blood Pressure and Vascular Function</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Effects of Beetroot Enriched Bread on Postprandial Vascular Function, Arterial Stiffness and Blood Pressure in Healthy Men</official_title>
